Broke many chains at Howlers' Notch.

Howlers' Notch, once a Warg den, is now a place of terrible holding-pens for the captured Azhorns as they are trained for war. Amongst the former warg dens, captured hill-beasts lie chained to rocks as they await their turn to be trained by the Gundabad Orcs. You should free these beasts before the Orcs get to them!
You have broken many chains at Howlers' Notch. Those in the war effort will be thankful for all that you have done here.
